reviews.review_text: My favorite version After streaming several songs on each version, this is the one I went with. This version has the best overall sound from what I could tell. They all sounded a little boomy to me. This one also has a nice split with Bob's guitar favoring one side and Brent's keyboard the other. The show itself is very good and has a nice setlist.
